1
00:00:22,480 --> 00:00:24,455
[Previously]
Immortal Force is sufficient.

2
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:25,879
Awaiting enlightenment of Artistic Conception.

3
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:28,239
to step into the middle stage of Inquiry Tripod.

4
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:31,319
Since you insist on dragging me
into this affair,

5
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:33,919
you must show sufficient sincerity.

6
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:35,759
They're here.

7
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:37,039
The Huan family has truly arrived.

8
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:39,119
Extinction.

9
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:41,279
I am a personal guard of Lady Huan Mei.

10
00:00:41,480 --> 00:00:42,480
If you harm me,

11
00:00:42,640 --> 00:00:44,359
Lady Huan Mei will never spare you.

12
00:00:46,400 --> 00:00:47,400
Friend Xu,

13
00:00:47,440 --> 00:00:48,479
Now that Huan Dong is dead,

14
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:50,279
the Huan family will surely investigate.

15
00:00:50,400 --> 00:00:51,400
Within three months,

16
00:00:51,480 --> 00:00:52,480
I will return.

17
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:54,920
Issue the command:

18
00:00:55,160 --> 00:00:56,160
Effective immediately,

19
00:00:56,760 --> 00:00:59,279
seal off all starry sky channels
of Ran Yun Star.

20
00:01:00,120 --> 00:01:01,399
Not a single ant

21
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:04,159
is to be allowed to escape this seat.

22
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:18,360
Death Qi...

23
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:20,999
The Goldflame Ore is a
yang-attributed treasure.

24
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,999
Upon this Cloud Glow Star,

25
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:25,199
why is the Death Qi so dense?

26
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:36,159
Cloud Glow Star is not a remote,
borderline location.

27
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:39,759
How is it that not a single trace
of human habitation exists?

28
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,560
That is...

29
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:55,960
Moon Gazer.

30
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,719
How can a Moon Gazer exist in this place?

31
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,999
In Tu Si's memories,

32
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:04,119
the Moon Gazer is a parasitic entity
unique to the Ancient God race,

33
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,599
surviving by sucking
the blood of Ancient Gods.

34
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:10,199
Moon Gazers cause no damage
to the massive Ancient God bodies;

35
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:13,919
they can even be driven
like magic treasures.

36
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,639
But once the Ancient God dies,

37
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:19,119
the Moon Gazers mostly
vanish into smoke.

38
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,959
Survival is nearly impossible.

39
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,239
Back then, Tu Si had passed away
for too long,

40
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,239
so that within the Land of the Ancient God,

41
00:02:26,440 --> 00:02:27,879
no traces of Moon Gazers remained.

42
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,639
Could it be that within
this Cloud Glow Star...

43
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,839
lies the remains of an
Ancient God corpse?

44
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:36,039
If that is truly the case,

45
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:38,399
how could the great powers
of the Rotating Sky Starfield

46
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,719
possibly turn a blind eye?

47
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,080
This place is strange.

48
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:44,439
I must find that Goldflame vein quickly.

49
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,879
It really is a Goldflame vein.

50
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:52,679
This...

51
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:55,439
This entire vein belongs to us?

52
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,199
Master,

53
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:58,079
we've struck it rich!

54
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,280
What are you waiting for?

55
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:00,639
At your command,

56
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,279
Little Xu Zi will start mining.

57
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:08,879
Wait.

58
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,999
This Goldflame vein...

59
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:12,599
is buried far too shallowly.

60
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,999
Any Inquiry Tripod cultivator

61
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,959
scanning casually could detect it.

62
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:19,839
Such a precious treasure—

63
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:22,199
how could it remain unclaimed
for millions of years?

64
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:24,600
Furthermore,

65
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:26,319
if it were naturally formed ore,

66
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,719
it should not be so pure
and orderly.

67
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:30,599
This substance...

68
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:33,279
resembles a section of bone.

69
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,280
It is not a tree.

70
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:42,959
It is a tentacle.

71
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,680
This Cloud Glow Star...

72
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:47,159
is a slumbering Moon Gazer

73
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:49,439
formed from an entire
Goldflame vein as its bone.

74
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:53,319
If we had tried to excavate
the Goldflame vein just now,

75
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:55,839
we would have surely startled
this Moon Gazer awake.

76
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,319
Facing such a colossal beast,

77
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,839
I would have no path to survival.

78
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,360
Throughout history,

79
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,919
all who mined the Goldflame vein

80
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:07,799
likely perished right here.

81
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:11,719
But the Goldflame vein is crucial
to the Rebellious Sky Pearl.

82
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,039
I am determined to obtain it.

83
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,639
As for how to extract it,

84
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:19,399
I must find another method.

85
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,560
Huan Mei.

86
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:42,119
After the blood exchange,

87
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,720
you

88
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,759
will truly become one of the Huan family.

89
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,319
In your actions and conduct,

90
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:52,359
do not fail the blood of the Huan family.

91
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:58,159
Square illusion as soul,

92
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,439
Myriad blood as guide.

93
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:03,999
Huan Wuqing of the Huan family's
twenty-sixth generation,

94
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,799
hereby beseeches

95
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,879
the ancestral spirit bloodline.

96
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,039
In the primordial past,

97
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:17,279
my Huan family were immortals
of the Thunder Immortal Realm.

98
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,719
Though the Immortal Realm is destroyed,

99
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,599
the bloodline remains.

100
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:24,279
This blood exchange ritual...

101
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,759
From tens of thousands of disciples' blood,

102
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:29,079
refine the purest bloodline.

103
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,879
Condensing it into a Blood Talisman
imprinted upon one person.

104
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,679
Today, this old ancestor

105
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:37,799
even lowered my own realm,

106
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:41,519
personally infusing vast amounts
of essence blood into this seal,

107
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,399
to cleanse her veins.

108
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,759
For her sake,

109
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,879
why must we pay such a price?

110
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,519
Myriad Illusions,

111
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,759
Formless.

112
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,999
The Old Ancestor's Myriad Illusion
Formless Dao

113
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:13,799
is the pinnacle of the Huan family,

114
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,399
yet it has no successor.

115
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:20,239
Could it be that the Old Ancestor's
grand commotion to bestow power

116
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:24,079
is to cultivate a successor
who possesses this Dao?

117
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,560
Impossible.

118
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:36,640
How could that be?

119
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,399
Her artistic conception...

120
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,719
is sublimating.

121
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,800
Sublimating!

122
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:45,319
The divine abilities of artistic conception
left to our clan by the ancient immortals—

123
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:48,039
the Heavenly Demon and Formless Paths.

124
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,359
Of these, the stronger Heavenly Demon Path

125
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,439
has long been lost.

126
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:54,239
Yet the artistic conception on this woman...

127
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,000
Could it be...

128
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:00,559
Artistic conception sublimation?

129
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,119
Unheard of!

130
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,399
So the Old Ancestor's scheme

131
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,559
was aimed at this.

132
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:14,679
Mei'er.

133
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,639
I thank the Old Ancestor
for the grace of recreation.

134
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,479
You truly did not disappoint

135
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:21,079
this old man's expectations.

136
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:24,039
Venerated Ancestors,

137
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,079
do you see this?

138
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:31,879
The Myriad Illusion Heavenly Demon Dao,
lost to the Huan family for eons,

139
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:34,319
has reappeared in the light of day!

140
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,120
Huan Mei.

141
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:41,159
This is your first battle
as a member of the Huan family.

142
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,839
Go to Ran Yun Star.

143
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,639
Slaughter your way to fame!

144
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,079
Don't waste your strength.

145
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,999
With just the three of us,

146
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,839
this Lockstar Grand Formation

147
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:01,280
cannot be broken.

148
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,599
Then what do we do?

149
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,439
If this formation isn't broken,

150
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,639
are we just to wait for death?

151
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:16,399
This move...

152
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:19,079
I'm afraid it is to establish Huan Mei's might.

153
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,999
Friend Xu Mu said

154
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,320
that in three months,

155
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,480
he will return.

156
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,639
Before the Huan family arrives,

157
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:27,679
that man will flee at the first sign of wind.

158
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:29,279
Will he really come back?

159
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:36,960
He's here.

160
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,999
The ancestors of the three Ran Yun clans...

161
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:46,959
Is it you?

162
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,360
She is...

163
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:51,760
Huan Mei.

164
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:54,959
My Ran Yun Star—

165
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:57,159
is it to be utterly destroyed

166
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,240
by a delicate woman?

167
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,879
Brother Sun, Brother Zhao,

168
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,479
now that disaster looms large,

169
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:07,519
let us simply fight with all we have.

170
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,239
Even in death,

171
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:11,559
we will have no regrets in this life.

172
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,119
Brother Ran is heroic.

173
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,879
Since you burn your Primordial Spirit,

174
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:15,919
I, Zhao,

175
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,319
will accompany you.

176
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,080
Enough.

177
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,120
I, Sun,

178
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,399
cannot lag behind.

179
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,679
I appreciate your resolve.

180
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:27,439
That you are willing to fight to the death

181
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:30,319
saves me a considerable amount of effort.

182
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,080
Dao Thought!

183
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:49,839
You...

184
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,639
Want to burn your Primordial Spirit?

185
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:53,759
Then burn it completely!

186
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:57,279
Brother Zhao!

187
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:58,400
Wake up!

188
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:03,800
Brother Sun!

189
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:05,279
Hurry, assist me!

190
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,320
Just what...

191
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,159
kind of Dao Thought is this?

192
00:10:22,183 --> 00:10:45,783
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

193
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:48,479
You could have clouded my mind,

194
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:51,319
yet you chose to keep me sober,

195
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:53,439
only to be brutally slaughtered
by allies.

196
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:57,039
What vicious methods.

197
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:58,400
This battle—

198
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,399
did I ever lift a finger?

199
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:03,159
You three fought each other.

200
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,559
What connection does it have
with me?

201
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:08,039
The Myriad Illusion
Heavenly Demon Dao.

202
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:10,359
I have never needed anyone to assist in battle.

203
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:12,679
Wherever I go,

204
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:15,119
countless cultivators fight for me.

205
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:18,119
And die for me.

206
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:29,359
With the abilities of you three,

207
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:32,279
it would be impossible to kill Huan Dong
without a sound.

208
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:34,520
At that time,

209
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:35,999
who else was present?

210
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:39,639
You three offered your main bodies
as sacrifices,

211
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:42,359
using the self-combustion of your
Primordial Spirits as a smokescreen.

212
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:45,039
Did you really think I couldn't see through it?

213
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:48,159
Did you leave behind avatars to preserve
your lives?

214
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:50,599
Please, spare my life!

215
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:51,919
That man was named Xu Mu.

216
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:52,919
At that time,

217
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:55,519
the one who killed your clan's
guard, Huan Dong, was him.

218
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:58,039
However, he left this place days ago.

219
00:11:58,640 --> 00:12:00,119
If you wish to find his traces,

220
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:00,639
I...

221
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:01,760
can help you.

222
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,080
No rush.

223
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,959
Once stained with the blood of the Huan family,

224
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,999
no one escapes.

225
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:17,999
Days ago, when I left,

226
00:12:18,760 --> 00:12:20,919
this Restriction did not exist on Ran Yun Star.

227
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,879
This formation is quite complex.

228
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:26,039
Breaking it will take some time.

229
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:29,359
But to barge into the formation—

230
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,440
that is not difficult.

231
00:12:43,040 --> 00:12:44,040
It's her.

232
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:46,159
Peak of Inquiry Tripod.

233
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:48,280
To fight her...

234
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:49,679
I have no certainty of victory.

235
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:53,119
But I used the Immortal Guard's method
to alter my appearance.

236
00:12:54,160 --> 00:12:55,719
She shouldn't be able to recognize me.

237
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,159
This true life-saving avatar—

238
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:59,199
I have never revealed its location
to anyone.

239
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:00,599
This woman...

240
00:13:00,800 --> 00:13:02,039
how on earth did she find me?

241
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:05,159
Self-combusting your Primordial Spirit,

242
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:07,439
yet falling into your own desires.

243
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,200
Fighting to the death,

244
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:10,959
yet leaving behind a life-saving avatar.

245
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:13,719
Your display of noble righteousness—

246
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:16,279
how much of it is real?

247
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,559
This is truly fascinating.

248
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,240
Friend Xu!

249
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:38,280
Save me!

250
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:39,720
Friend Sun!

251
00:13:40,040 --> 00:13:41,239
You had an avatar,

252
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:43,039
yet you didn't inform me?

253
00:13:43,400 --> 00:13:44,400
This...

254
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:47,679
I imagine you were scheming to have me
fight the Huan family to the death.

255
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:49,400
Regardless of success,

256
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:52,039
you could use these avatars to survive.

257
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:53,760
Did I get that right?

258
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:56,359
Though you lacked benevolence,

259
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:58,799
since I accepted your Immortal Jade,

260
00:13:59,400 --> 00:14:00,799
I shall protect you this once.

261
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,839
I advise you not to meddle further.

262
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:08,720
Now,

263
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:10,719
leave Ran Yun Star.

264
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,679
Unexpected.

265
00:14:26,280 --> 00:14:28,479
Your cultivation has actually reached
the Inquiry Tripod realm.

266
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:32,119
You really thought that by masking
your appearance,

267
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:34,159
and altering your aura,

268
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,399
I wouldn't recognize you?

269
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:37,920
Wang Lin.

270
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,959
But early Inquiry Tripod...

271
00:14:43,160 --> 00:14:45,639
you are destined to perish here.

272
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,559
Back on Vermilion Bird Star,

273
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:52,479
when you destroyed my Artistic Conception,

274
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,839
I used the Myriad Illusions
Heartless Art

275
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:56,839
to glimpse your Obsessive Desire.

276
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:59,040
Today,

277
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:01,319
I shall only destroy your Dao Heart,

278
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:03,079
and shatter your Obsessive Desire,

279
00:15:03,760 --> 00:15:05,119
to vent my hatred!

280
00:15:12,920 --> 00:15:13,920
Wang Lin.

281
00:15:14,360 --> 00:15:15,360
I shall send you

282
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,199
to reunite with that Li Muwan.

283
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:19,079
Seeking death!

284
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:01,519
What kind of sorcery is this?

285
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:03,999
Observing with Divine Sense,

286
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:06,599
this person seems just like Hongdie.

287
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,240
Just an illusion.

288
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:11,999
Putting on a mystical show.

289
00:16:17,520 --> 00:16:18,520
Uncle...

290
00:16:18,800 --> 00:16:19,119
You...

291
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:21,599
You want to kill Little Rujiu?

292
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:22,800
Illusion.

293
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:24,599
This is also an illusion.

294
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:25,679
Disciple,

295
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:30,439
remember to pass down the
Soul Banner Art.

296
00:16:31,400 --> 00:16:33,479
Spread the Soul Refining Sect

297
00:16:34,040 --> 00:16:35,679
and carry it to greatness.

298
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:37,320
Wang Lin.

299
00:16:39,280 --> 00:16:40,280
Brother...

300
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:42,639
Illusion.

301
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:43,960
Son.

302
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:55,960
Senior Brother.

303
00:16:57,480 --> 00:16:58,480
Return.

304
00:17:07,760 --> 00:17:09,319
Myriad Illusion Heavenly Demon Dao.

305
00:17:10,120 --> 00:17:11,599
Borrowing the opponent's memories,

306
00:17:12,080 --> 00:17:13,639
igniting the fire of the Primordial Spirit,

307
00:17:14,280 --> 00:17:15,599
burning the body and mind.

308
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:18,079
Waiting for the mind to lapse,

309
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:20,719
so one becomes a fish on the chopping block.

310
00:17:21,840 --> 00:17:22,840
Wang Lin.

311
00:17:23,320 --> 00:17:25,679
The fire of your Primordial Spirit
is already lit.

312
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:27,240
The outcome

313
00:17:27,800 --> 00:17:29,119
is already decided.

314
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:39,640
Thunder...

315
00:17:39,880 --> 00:17:41,119
In his Primordial Spirit,

316
00:17:41,120 --> 00:17:42,559
how can there be Thunder power?

317
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:45,800
How is this possible?

318
00:17:46,760 --> 00:17:47,999
When causality is settled,

319
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:50,159
and the heart holds no regrets,

320
00:17:51,080 --> 00:17:52,759
one may return to silence.

321
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:54,799
But if causality is unfinished,

322
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:57,519
even facing the Will of Heaven,

323
00:17:58,520 --> 00:17:59,919
one must defy it.

324
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:02,079
During the Inquiry Tripod stage,

325
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:03,599
I comprehended this Dao.

326
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,000
My Obsessive Desire—

327
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:09,359
how could it be restrained
by your mere Artistic Conception?

328
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:14,959
Though your cultivation
was forcibly elevated,

329
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:16,399
your Artistic Conception

330
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:17,239
is worlds apart.

331
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:18,400
is worlds apart.

332
00:18:27,280 --> 00:18:28,079
Your Artistic Conception

333
00:18:28,080 --> 00:18:29,639
cannot break Wang's Dao Heart.

334
00:18:30,840 --> 00:18:31,999
Your Illusion Arts

335
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:34,559
cannot burn

336
00:18:34,560 --> 00:18:36,119
Wang's Primordial Spirit.

337
00:18:36,143 --> 00:19:14,443
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

